{"tid":2387125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"GameStop事件　代表散戶上電視　妙語連珠　下下打中華爾街建制","createTime":"2021-01-30T05:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T06:28:28.000Z","uid":261647,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1dab0b44fd99256d13b1e5186ad16f87c22e2a14","tid":2387125,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ranke.wang.5/posts/2924990737737601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Franke.wang.5%2Fposts%2F2924990737737601&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjKkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=dc42e258\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ranke.wang.5/posts/2924990737737601</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5km6nC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5km6nC.png&h=d2b4581b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Ranke<br />\n<br />\nGameStop嘎空的幕後<br />\n<br />\nCNBC邀請Chamath上電視展開的討論GameStop(GME US)，不認識Chamath自己維基一下(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chamath_Palihapitiya\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChamath_Palihapitiya&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjKkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=166e401b\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chamath_Palihapitiya</a>)，這個年代不再是巴菲特的年代，而屬於Musk、Chamath這樣大破大立的人物。不論你是否同意，新一代的年輕人就是這麼想。<br />\n<br />\nChamath不但有眾多粉絲，而且還在推特上帶頭買GME，他因此被邀請上電視作為散戶代表。CNBC希望用道德拷問Chamath，打掉這群造反派的氣焰。<br />\n<br />\n再好的文字，也很難形容Chamath在電視上嘴爆CNBC主持人的精彩。稍微摘要一下：<br />\n<br />\n1. GME股價暴漲的原因是這檔股票被機構做空了140%，憑什麼可以多40%？要不是華爾街機構天天利用散戶不能用的工具，怎麼可能多40%而被散戶抓到把柄？讚！<br />\n<br />\n2. 論壇上的研究水準，很多都和避險基金的研究水準相當，憑什麼散戶不能根據這些研究來買賣？讚！<br />\n<br />\n3. 華爾街的量化基金（點名去年大賠的文藝復興），根本就不看基本面來買賣，憑什麼他們不看基本面就可以不受到指責，而散戶不看基本面就要被指責？讚！<br />\n<br />\n4. 從特斯拉股價的歷史來看，所有的避險基金都錯，所有的散戶都對，憑什麼說避險基金就一定會比散戶正確？讚！(Chamath是最早重壓特斯拉的避險基金經理之一)<br />\n<br />\n5. 避險基金只開放給大戶投資而不開放給散戶，現在散戶賺錢了就不滿了要限制散戶，憑什麼？還是讚！<br />\n<br />\n本來以為是個對散戶的道德拷問，最後卻變成了對股票市場建制派的靈魂拷問！<br />\n<br />\nChamath也說得很清楚，市場中性策略（market neutral）基金靠著10億美元的本金，就能得到券商100億美元的杠杆，這些都是散戶沒有的優勢。華爾街就靠著秘密，靠著好的晚餐，靠著相互之間勾肩搭背，來壟斷投資市場。而論壇的討論很透明，這些都是華爾街應該學習的東西。<br />\n<br />\n#作掉一個川普還有千千萬萬個川普"},{"pid":"645f29b031f41c978eeb64a8000950f4b8d10b48","tid":2387125,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"係講得好"},{"pid":"55eb2c0a5425400879809e23fa194772f63d2c00","tid":2387125,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa105c6ec390356efff742ca56cd6f892151b4e7","tid":2387125,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21f89665747d6ca5baf00b23bc1fda0a74ca346","tid":2387125,"uid":187956,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"事實上好多hedge fund又跑輸大市<br />\n又唔撚透明 真心所有fund應該好似ark咁管理<br />\n每日send trade reports 分享ideas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />散戶可以自行決定買/賣"},{"pid":"e71f68eee38d0612dc7e9cd2bb6a575c9c646c2e","tid":2387125,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"又係140%<br />\n沽空d貨冇人買咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預咗你地負評"},{"pid":"ecf401afe627e5b223ea8296c0483d1c1136a257","tid":2387125,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}